tmjstore (2.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * REWRITE COMPLETA EM RUST. TMJStore agora e Rust + gtk4-rs +
    libadwaita (era Python + PyGObject).
  * Single binary /usr/bin/tmjstore. Zero dependencia Python.
  * 3 abas: Apps, Instalados, Atualizacoes (Adw ViewStack).
  * Detail page com metadata AppStream, release history.
  * Install/remove/upgrade async via pkexec + apt-get.

